quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,90,Wa Laqad Qāla Lahum Hārūnu Min Qablu Yā Qawmi 'Innamā Futintum Bihi Wa 'Inna Rabbakumu Ar-Raĥmānu Fa Attabi`ūnī Wa 'Aţī`ū 'Amrī
  20,91,Qālū Lan Nabraĥa `Alayhi `Ākifīna Ĥattá Yarji`a 'Ilaynā Mūsá
  20,92,Qāla Yā Hārūnu Mā Mana`aka 'Idh Ra'aytahum Đallū
  20,93,Allā Tattabi`anī 'Afa`aşayta 'Amrī
  20,94,Qāla Yabna'uumma Lā Ta'khudh Biliĥyatī Wa Lā Bira'sī 'Innī Khashītu 'An Taqūla Farraqta Bayna Banī 'Isrā'īla Wa Lam Tarqub Qawlī
  20,95,Qāla Famā Khaţbuka Yā Sāmirīyu
  20,96,Qāla Başurtu Bimā Lam Yabşurū Bihi Faqabađtu Qabđatan Min 'Athari Ar-Rasūli Fanabadhtuhā Wa Kadhalika Sawwalat Lī Nafsī
  20,97,Qāla Fādh/hab Fa'inna Laka Fī Al-Ĥayāati 'An Taqūla Lā Misāsa Wa 'Inna Laka Maw`idāan Lan Tukhlafahu Wa Anžur 'Ilá 'Ilahika Al-Ladhī Žalta `Alayhi `Ākifāan Lanuĥarriqannahu Thumma Lanansifannahu Fī Al-Yammi Nasfāan
  20,98,Innamā 'Ilahukumu Allāhu Al-Ladhī Lā 'Ilāha 'Illā Huwa Wasi`a Kulla Shay'in `Ilmāan
  20,99,Kadhālika Naquşşu `Alayka Min 'Anbā'i Mā Qad Sabaqa Wa Qad 'Ātaynāka Min Ladunnā Dhikrāan
  20,100,Man 'A`rađa `Anhu Fa'innahu Yaĥmilu Yawma Al-Qiyāmati Wizrāan
  20,101,Khālidīna Fīhi Wa Sā'a Lahum Yawma Al-Qiyāmati Ĥimlāan
  20,102,Yawma Yunfakhu Fī Aş-Şūri Wa Naĥshuru Al-Mujrimīna Yawma'idhin Zurqāan
  20,103,Yatakhāfatūna Baynahum 'In Labithtum 'Illā `Ashrāan
  20,104,Naĥnu 'A`lamu Bimā Yaqūlūna 'Idh Yaqūlu 'Amthaluhum Ţarīqatan 'In Labithtum 'Illā Yawmāan